# Data Model

## Objects Used

### Account

Stores company information.

| Field        | Type     |
| ------------ | -------- |
| Account Name | Text     |
| Industry     | Picklist |
| Phone        | Phone    |
| Website      | URL      |

---

### Contact

Stores customer information.

| Field      | Type  |
| ---------- | ----- |
| First Name | Text  |
| Last Name  | Text  |
| Email      | Email |
| Phone      | Phone |

---

### Opportunity

Stores sales opportunity information.

| Field            | Type     |
| ---------------- | -------- |
| Opportunity Name | Text     |
| Stage            | Picklist |
| Amount           | Currency |
| Close Date       | Date     |

---

## Relationships

```text
Account
   │
   ├── Contact
   │
   └── Opportunity
```

### Relationship Explanation

* One Account can have multiple Contacts.
* One Account can have multiple Opportunities.
* Contacts are associated with Accounts.
* Opportunities represent potential revenue.

