# Apex Logic

Apex is used for advanced business logic that cannot be handled by Flow alone.

## Example Apex Class

```apex
public with sharing class OpportunityController {

    @AuraEnabled
    public static List<Opportunity> getOpportunities() {

        return [
            SELECT Id, Name, Amount, StageName
            FROM Opportunity
            LIMIT 10
        ];
    }
}
```

### Purpose

* Retrieve Opportunity records.
* Supply data to Lightning Web Components.
* Support dashboard functionality.

---

## Example Trigger Logic

```apex
trigger OpportunityTrigger on Opportunity (before insert) {

    for(Opportunity opp : Trigger.new) {

        if(opp.Amount < 0) {
            opp.addError('Amount cannot be negative.');
        }
    }
}
```

### Purpose

Prevent invalid opportunity amounts from being saved.

